Title: Adalen 31
Actors: Peter Schildt, Kerstin Tidelius, Roland Hedlund, Stefan Feierbach
Plot: During a strike strike-breakers are being transported to Lunde, where they are assaulted by the strikers. The military are sent in. On the 14th May 1931 there is a confrontation between demonstrators and the military who open fire and five people are killed and five injured.
Awards: Nominated for 1 Oscar. Another 6 wins & 3 nominations.
